what_you_do: Rezarta Tabaku is a coach who empowers women leaders and helps them become more influential and impactful.
who_you_serve: Women who feel undervalued and underappreciated in their corporate careers.
social_proof: Rezarta has overcome significant challenges in her own life, including being a single mother raising a child with special needs, an immigrant navigating a new country and language, and experiencing trauma. Despite these setbacks, she has achieved an executive position and is now on a mission to help other women achieve their full potential.
signature_programs: Woman of Influence (private coaching) and Leader of Impact (private coaching)
business_focus: Empowering women leaders to become more influential and impactful in their careers and lives.
